  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Life Skills and Independence for 60 Adults</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Diya Foundation provides free Life-skills and Work skills training to around 60 adults with intellectual challenges preparing them to be self dependent and self confident adults. Once a basic schooling program is over most of these young adults have very few options for training on work and life skills. In the past sixteen years, Diya has seen many, many life altering moments from being unable to bathe, shave, sit at a task to being independent and proud of earning and contributing to family.</narrative>
  </description>
